<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.eoearth.org/article/Soddy,_Frederick" class="external free" title="http://www.eoearth.org/article/Soddy,_Frederick" rel="nofollow">http://www.eoearth.org/article/Soddy,_Frederick</a> Soddy, Frederick - Encyclopedia of Earth</li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/12/opinion/12zencey.html?_r=1&amp;ref=opinion" class="external text" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/12/opinion/12zencey.html?_r=1&amp;ref=opinion" rel="nofollow">Eric Zencey, "Mr. Soddy’s Ecological Economy", <i>The New York Times</i>, Opinion Section, April 12, 2009.</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFBurleyFoster.2C_John1994">Burley, Peter; Foster, John (1994). <i>Economics and Thermodynamics – New Perspectives on Economic Analysis</i>. Kluwer Academic Publishers. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0792394461" class="internal">ISBN 0-7923-9446-1</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Economics+and+Thermodynamics+%E2%80%93+New+Perspectives+on+Economic+Analysis&amp;rft.aulast=Burley&amp;rft.aufirst=Peter&amp;rft.au=Burley%2C+Peter&amp;rft.au=Foster%2C+John&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.pub=Kluwer+Academic+Publishers&amp;rft.isbn=0-7923-9446-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Thermoeconomics"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://telstar.ote.cmu.edu/environ/m3/s3/05account.shtml" class="external free" title="http://telstar.ote.cmu.edu/environ/m3/s3/05account.shtml" rel="nofollow">http://telstar.ote.cmu.edu/environ/m3/s3/05account.shtml</a> Environmental Decision making, Science and Technology</li>
<li id="cite_note-Baumarter-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Baumarter_12-0" title="">^</a></b> Baumgarter, Stefan. (2004). <a href="http://www.eco.uni-heidelberg.de/ng-oeoe/research/papers/Baumgaertner%202004%20ModEE.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.eco.uni-heidelberg.de/ng-oeoe/research/papers/Baumgaertner%202004%20ModEE.pdf" rel="nofollow">Thermodynamic Models</a>, Modeling in Ecological Economics (Ch. 18)</li>
